data.title: Michelle Seibert - 2008-09 - Track & Field
data.meta_description:
Michelle SeibertMiddle Distance  - Junior: Redshirted the 2007-08 seasons ... 
Sophomore: Competed on the indoor DMR team that ran the second-best time in school
data.text:
Junior: Redshirted the 2007-08 seasons ...

Sophomore: Competed on the indoor DMR team that ran the second-best time in school history at the Tyson Invitational ... ran the 800m leg of the DMR for the ACC Championship team ... competed on the indoor NCAA DMR team ... member of the outdoor 4x400m relay that qualified for ECAC Championships ... ran a best of 2:07.8 in the 800m at the outdoor ACC Championships and finished fourth ... led off the 4x800m relay at Penn Relays that went on to set a school record ... also ran on the DMR at Penn Relays that set the No. 3 all-time Duke record ... qualified for finals of the ECAC Championships and qualified for the NCAA Regional meet ...

Freshman: Ran third-fastest 500m in Duke history and qualified for ECAC Indoor Championships with a time of 1:15.17 ... finished 14th at USATF Junior Outdoor Championships in 800m ... red-shirted indoor and outdoor track season...
